net.sf.jclec.mo.problem.zdt

Class ZDT3F2Objective

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jclec.mo.evaluation.Objective
      • net.sf.jclec.mo.problem.zdt.ZDT3F2Objective
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, net.sf.jclec.IConfigure, net.sf.jclec.JCLEC

    public class ZDT3F2Objective
extends Objective
    F2 function of ZDT3 optimization problem. For a definition of the ZDT3 problem, see:

    Paper: E. Ziztler, K. Deb, L. Thiele. "Comparison of Multiobjective Evolutionary Algorithms: Empirical Results". Evolutionary Computation, vol. 8, no. 2, pp. 173-195. 2000.

    URL: http://people.ee.ethz.ch/~sop/download/supplementary/testproblems/zdt3/

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
